    "description": "Bank of America's Responsible AI Framework, published in 2024, governs every customer-facing model. The framework includes mandatory fairness testing for credit-decisioning AI (independent third-party audited), transparency disclosures on every AI-assisted recommendation, and a 90-day customer right-of-appeal on any AI-influenced decision affecting account access or product eligibility.",
